	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S[alutem] p[lurimam].</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="place367">Friburgo</placeName> <placeName ref="place367">Brisgoiae</placeName> per <placeName ref="place97">Basileam</placeName> in Burgundiam rediens,<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><persName ref="person20061">Cousin</persName> lebte in <placeName ref="place1598">Nozeroy</placeName> (Dép. Jura), wo er sich Ende 1535 niedergelassen hatte.</note> vir clarissime, quum <persName ref="person74">Gastius</persName> noster nuncium<note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3">Unbekannt.</note> Tigurum se cras<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a">cras <hi>über der Zeile nachgetragen.</hi></note><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Der Brief, dem ein Geschenk für Bullinger beigelegt war (s. unten Anm. 11), verließ <placeName ref="place97">Basel</placeName> erst am 14. März 1545 oder kurz darauf; s. unten <ref target="file12156">Nr. 2109</ref>, 1-3.</note> missurum diceret, et me, si quid vellem, rogaret, nolui committere, ut is sine meis literis abiret mei in te animi significatricibus, tametsi de mea adversum te observantia nihil te dubitare credam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Pro benignitate autem tua, qua me quam plurimis annis perpetuo complecteris, tibi gratias ago immortales.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cuius quidem nuper in aperienda candide mihi tua de eucharistia sententia specimen<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Bullingers verlorene Antwort auf <persName ref="person20061">Cousins</persName> Brief, in dem er auf <persName ref="person20061">Cousins</persName> Anfrage seine Meinung über das Abendmahl darlegt hatte; s. HBBW XIV, <ref target="file11974">Nr. 1927</ref> und Anm. 15.</note> quoque praebuisti.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam is sim, mi Bullingere, qui aliquando non ingratum me declarare possim!</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Voluntas, ita me deus amet, nunquam deest; quam si re ipsa factis pręstare non potero<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6">Vgl. Röm 7, 16.</note> - cum maior sis, quam quo conatus nostri adspirare valent -<pb type="edition" next="178"/> conatum tamen laudabis, quando in magnis, ut ille<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Sextus Propertius (<persName ref="person1876">Properz</persName>) aus Assisi (ca. 50 bis ca. 15 v. Chr).</note> inquit, vel voluisse sat est<note xml:id="fn8" type="footnote" n="8">Vgl. <hi><persName ref="person1876">Properz</persName>,</hi> Elegiae, 2, 10, 5; in Adagia, 2,S. 55 (ASD II/4 184, <ref target="file11801">Nr. 1755</ref>).</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mi Bullingere, cura, quoad potes, ut valeas, sicque existimes nihil nobis tua valetudine iucundius, nihil ęque gratius adnunciari posse.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="place97">Basileę</placeName>, 4. idus martii anno christiano 1545, praepropere, ut vides.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="person74">Gastio</persName> commisi ad te munus<note xml:id="fn9" type="footnote" n="9">Ein Hemd aus einem Mischgewebe mit Seide; s. unten <ref target="file12225">Nr. 2178</ref>, 3.</note>; id ut boni consulas, etiam atque etiam rogo.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Amicis omnibus s[alutem] p[lurimam], imprimis <persName ref="person14">Bibliandro</persName> et Guesnero.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex animo tuus <persName ref="person20061">Gilbertus</persName> Cognatus Nozeręus<note xml:id="fnb" type="footnote" n="b"><hi>Ansonsten bezeichnet sich <persName ref="person20061">Cousin</persName> als</hi> Nozerenus.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Domino Henrico Bullingero, verę theologię ac christianismi vindici incomparabili, domino et praeceptori suo observando.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tiguri.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
